These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: mystery, epic, horror, documentary, scientific, animation, action
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, montecristo, prince, bongani, pall-mall, vegafina, alhambra
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, rock, soul, indie, jazz, folk, hip-hop
 1. the person watching action movies is the vegafina-smoker##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
 4. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
 5. the person watching animation movies is the person watching animation movies##1
 6. the fan of rock is the aristoff-smoker##1
 7. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
 8. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 9. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
10. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
11. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1
12. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
13. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
14. the person watching animation movies is in an even position##4
15. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
16. the vegafina-smoker is in an odd position##4
17. the fan of soul is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
18. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
19. the fan of rock is the person watching animation movies##1
20. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7     |
| Movie-Genre      | action  | epic | horror | animation        | mystery       | documentary | scientific     |
| Cigar   | vegafina   | alhambra       | prince  | aristoff  | bongani  | montecristo   | pall-mall  |
| Music-Genre         | hip-hop | jazz         | folk  | rock | disco | indie  | soul |

