 2. the person playing bridge is the person drinking water##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
 4. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the turkish##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the left of the dutch##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 9. the mexican is on the right of the brazilian##1
10. the person playing monopoly is the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
13. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
14. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
15. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
16. the argentine is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
17. the pakistani is in an even position##4
18. the dutch is the person drinking water##1
19. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
20. the person playing go is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |       3       |     4      |   5    |       6        |   7    |
