10. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
11. the person who likes lavender is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
12. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
13. the person who likes ebony is in the middle##1
14. the person traveling to london is between the person who likes light-blue and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
15. the person who growstulip is in the middle##1
16. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
17. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
